    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive with confidence! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and dependable ride. It\u2019s a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a reliable, high-quality car that\u2019s ready for the road!",
