      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and displaying no signs of wear, this example represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality, this is an investment-grade opportunity that delivers a new-car experience at a sophisticated value.",
