      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and presented in showroom condition, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of excellence rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. We invite you to acquire a specimen that transcends the ordinary.",
      "price": 48500.0,
